@IchiHimeKUROSAKI  I think I've said it before, but people aren't complaining because it's NTR, but because no Arakure story makes sense or coherence, especially this one.

A lot of NTR artists, including Arakure, have a problem, and that is that they believe that just by making NTR content, they justify bad writing.

Now, if you're one of those who prefers to only watch sexual scenes without caring about the story, good for you, be happy jerking off.
